Program.Title: Advanced Manufacturing Level III-CERT
Program.Description: This certificate in Advanced Manufacturing Level III covers the introduction and principles of ERP software for manufacturing, introduction to robotic welding, 3D modeling to production, and an internship with local trade company.  Safety principles are always practiced, as well as trade licensure preparation and manufacturing guidelines used in the industry.
